HEADWORD: Dentated
<hw>Den"ta*ted</hw>
<pr>(d⟦ecr⟧n"t⟦asl⟧*t⟦ecr⟧d)</pr>, }</mhw> <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>dentatus</ets>, fr. <ets>dens</ets>, <ets>dentis</ets>,
tooth.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>Toothed; especially,
with the teeth projecting straight out, not pointed either forward or
